┌─────── Keybindings ────────┐
│ Playback                   │
│   Space         Play / pau │
│   + / =         Speed up   │
│   -             Speed down │
│                            │
│ Navigation                 │
│   ← →           Seek ±5s   │
│   Shift+← →     Seek ±30s  │
│   . ,           Step forwa │
│   ] [           Next / pre │
│   0-9           Jump to 0% │
│   Home / g      Jump to st │
│   End / G       Jump to en │
└────────────────────────────┘
